enhanced_by.reason: Both methods modify the internal state of the Safelist by adding tags or attributes.
Both methods involve adding attributes to tags, though addEnforcedAttribute specifically enforces a value.
The method getEnforcedAttributes retrieves the enforced attributes, which can be used to verify the results of addEnforcedAttribute.
Both methods deal with attribute safety and can be used to assert that the added enforced attribute is correctly handled.
